    "For instance, the Kurjak Antenatal Neurodevelopmental Test (KANET), supported by AI, evaluates fetal motor responses and brain development, offering clinicians an early window into potential developmental disorders [33,39].AI systems also enhance epigenetic research by linking environmental factors to specific molecular changes [10,22]."
